When It comes to writing, world building is key. But when you have over a dozen 
seperate storylines in play, each as complex as the other, Things can get 
mighty confusing. So how do we keep them all straight? Introducing Herobase, the
fully functional prototype story keeper for the amatuer writer. As one myself,
I am designing the site to help keep my own stories straight in an easy and 
understandable way. However, The design can be adapted for any writer, as long
as they have basic knowledge of SQl and database creation.